quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  27,77,"Wa-innahu lahudan warahmatunlilmu/mineen"
  27,78,"Inna rabbaka yaqdee baynahum bihukmihiwahuwa alAAazeezu alAAaleem"
  27,79,"Fatawakkal AAala Allahi innakaAAala alhaqqi almubeen"
  27,80,"Innaka la tusmiAAu almawta walatusmiAAu assumma adduAAaa ithawallaw mudbireen"
  27,81,"Wama anta bihadee alAAumyiAAan dalalatihim in tusmiAAu illa manyu/minu bi-ayatina fahum muslimoon"
  27,82,"Wa-itha waqaAAa alqawlu AAalayhimakhrajna lahum dabbatan mina al-arditukallimuhum anna annasa kanoo bi-ayatinala yooqinoon"
  27,83,"Wayawma nahshuru min kulli ommatinfawjan mimman yukaththibu bi-ayatinafahum yoozaAAoon"
  27,84,"Hatta itha jaooqala akaththabtum bi-ayatee walam tuheetoobiha AAilman ammatha kuntum taAAmaloon"
  27,85,"WawaqaAAa alqawlu AAalayhim bima thalamoofahum la yantiqoon"
  27,86,"Alam yaraw anna jaAAalnaallayla liyaskunoo feehi wannahara mubsiraninna fee thalika laayatin liqawmin yu/minoon"
  27,87,"Wayawma yunfakhu fee assoorifafaziAAa man fee assamawati waman feeal-ardi illa man shaa Allahu wakullunatawhu dakhireen"
  27,88,"Watara aljibala tahsabuhajamidatan wahiya tamurru marra assahabi sunAAaAllahi allathee atqana kulla shay-in innahukhabeerun bima tafAAaloon"
